00:47:04.059 --> 00:47:06.030
It has a radial node. Right?
 

00:47:06.030 --> 00:47:08.617
Or pardon me,
yes, a radial or a spherical

00:47:08.617 --> 00:47:11.079
node here, that surrounds the
sphere.

00:47:11.079 --> 00:47:14.840
So it's red sign inside,
blue sign outside.

00:47:14.840 --> 00:47:20.063
The same thing is true of the
NH_3, but you have to rotate in

00:47:20.063 --> 00:47:21.630
