protons are,

00:48:28.679 --> 00:48:31.960
the fundamental shape was from
the kinetic energy.

00:48:31.960 --> 00:48:34.519
It was like the
3d_x^2-y^2.

00:48:34.519 --> 00:48:36.079
Or how about this one?
 

00:48:36.079 --> 00:48:40.688
There you can see -- but it's
