thing.

00:48:43.559 --> 00:48:48.039
But the ones on top have been
pulled out by the protons.

00:48:48.039 --> 00:48:49.010
Or this one.
 

00:48:49.010 --> 00:48:52.030
That's the one that has a
doughnut around the middle.

00:48:52.030 --> 00:48:56.501
But the doughnut has been
pulled down by the three

00:48:56.501 --> 00:48:59.969
hydrogens that aren't on the z
axis.

00:48:59.969 --> 00:49:02.650
Or there it is, rotated.
 

00:49:02.650 --> 00:49:03.480
Okay?
 

